                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18140112-31-defend323 t18140112-31-punish168"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>, aged 51.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. Justice Dallas.</p>
